reviewText: I love Iggy Pop so I loved the movie !!!
"I bet you're not wearing any panties."-Iggy Pop. Seriously, this movie was pretty good. Cyborg Iggy needs to come back for the sequel.
A beautiful film....  YES. I mean beautiful, the local is beautiful and Kacey Clarke is a REAL star!!!  Write that name down, remember it, tell your children....  Kacey Clarke is the real deal!!!
Wasn't quite what I was expecting but Iggy was awesome! If you're an Iggy Poo fan get it!!!
Love this film. Iggy does a masterful job. Funny, sexy, dark, twisted. What more could I ask for? Everyone in it was good.
